            witness role <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">models</ENAMEX>) as well as the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">community</ENAMEX> based
            <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">organization</ENAMEX> level. All lay health <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">advisors</ENAMEX> and witness
            role <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">models</ENAMEX> received formal training about the informed
