            <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> practiced obtaining informed consent from
            each other (using the consent form for the <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Witness</ENAMEX>
            Project of <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Buffalo</ENAMEX>) under the supervision of <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Witness</ENAMEX>
            Project <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">staff</ENAMEX>. Trainees critiqued each others'
